"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640643615,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"Lj-Sx5PkwdFuC04g2btgQQDjuoYxYA-RO31mH_q-urE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xc198c8a81bB6CeFF7d0ef1Beb32B4B8b1eF8baF5\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Vxi86_B_bf7ns3j__AFoM6u5nzln9Pychgn1CVkbTHI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"k8zBRXoQhTQ6KsYxR_EhyDIRwkzRbLKplnmLi6fq4Mg\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"FgbAQdm8k06Hvg8lL8FXxdws3OLZVQvyRmtuO80vLbR5I6e_OuTyw_s9D-4m8rKsDDNpz76Fsb1-btrPY9AWbg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xd407d651958dccd3afe82fc609673809896bdde33298a2eca31db3a9e4e693ef492517d371af4279c71b89ac1f421c0db2d718af7565560f6330239f3fb71bbf1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Vxi86_B_bf7ns3j__AFoM6u5nzln9Pychgn1CVkbTHI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"k8zBRXoQhTQ6KsYxR_EhyDIRwkzRbLKplnmLi6fq4Mg\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi